The paper focuses on the development of a computer vision algorithm for vehicle detection using UAVs, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning techniques, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the optimization of the algorithm for deployment on low-power embedded processors, which falls under the category of neural engineering (cs.NE).
